<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: sans-serif; background-color: #f8fafc; padding: 40px; margin: 0; }
        .container { background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 20px; padding: 40px; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
        .logo { font-weight: 900; font-size: 24px; color: #10b981; letter-spacing: -1px; margin-bottom: 40px; }
        h1 { font-weight: 900; font-size: 20px; color: #0f172a; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        p { color: #64748b; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 15px; }
        .receipt { border: 2px dashed #e2e8f0; border-radius: 15px; padding: 25px; margin: 30px 0; }
        .receipt-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9; padding-bottom: 10px; }
        .label { font-weight: bold; color: #94a3b8; font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .value { font-weight: 900; color: #0f172a; }
        .button { display: inline-block; background-color: #10b981; color: #ffffff; padding: 18px 35px; border-radius: 12px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-top: 20px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="logo">ImmoPro.</div>
        <h1>Confirmation de paiement reçu</h1>
        <p>Bonjour {{ user.name }},</p>
        <p>Votre paiement de loyer a bien été enregistré dans notre système.</p>
        
        <div class="receipt">
            <div class="receipt-row">
                <span class="label">Période</span>
                <span class="value">{{ paiement.dateEcheance|date('F Y') }}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="receipt-row">
                <span class="label">Montant</span>
                <span class="value">{{ paiement.montantLoyer|number_format(0, ',', ' ') }} GNF</span>
            </div>
            <div class="receipt-row">
                <span class="label">Date de paiement</span>
                <span class="value">{{ paiement.datePaiement|date('d/m/Y') }}</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <a href="#" class="button">Télécharger votre quittance</a>
        <p style="margin-top: 40px; font-size: 12px; color: #cbd5e1;">Merci de votre ponctualité. L'équipe ImmoPro.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
